{"tid":185792,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[神作]未聞花名 真人版","createTime":"2017-04-03T17:00:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T11:33:55.000Z","uid":56833,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e1648f10bc63b17a38fd3901a022357798a3fa6","tid":185792,"uid":56833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T17:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RTM5T8X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRTM5T8X.jpg&h=0ecc1bc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0yOoM86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0yOoM86.jpg&h=ffdd785f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n劇情介紹:<br />\n<br />\n昔日總是結伴遊玩的青梅竹馬，卻在升上高中之後彼此有了距離，家裡蹲男主角「仁太」、很有一般女高中生感覺的「鳴子」、進入升學高中的「雪集」與「鶴子」、沒有繼續升學而展開旅行的「波波」&hellip;&hellip;某天，本應離世的芽衣子出現在仁太面前，並忽然間說有「想要實現的願望」而拜託仁太，以此為契機，分散在各處的大家又再次地聚集在一起，實現芽衣子的願望，並在過程中相互解開心結&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://myself-bbs.com/thread-38822-1-1.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmyself-bbs.com%2Fthread-38822-1-1.htm&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9Nr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=c3904839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://myself-bbs.com/thread-38822-1-1.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n呢套野還原左好多動畫入邊既經典位 真人版黎講真係算高質 尤其係D演員 <br />\n<br />\n面麻 好可愛呀!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b76e5cec545dfdc10f3bb08489e8915a12748c","tid":185792,"uid":56833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T17:02:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"487ae7f2e0c8f8f9e2e0d9b8678e5d1dbcd5e658","tid":185792,"uid":56833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T17:05:05.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"bbb46dfa49e7a6e63ac8d21b339f5b22f70097af","tid":185792,"uid":56833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T17:05:15.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"8